	(53,28,'cake_details','Our family is kind of out of control large, so we use Grandma\'s birthday as an excuse to have family reunions.  Last year was my Grandma\'s 92nd birthday and somehow over the years aquired the nickname <q>Grandma Sunshine</q>, so naturally she needed a sunshine cake. Her favorite shirt is a black and white paisely print so that got thrown on there for an added bonus.'),
